metadata.name: Cornelius
metadata.description:
I know of a well-respected man;
who never cease to pray.
Many times I have wondered what keeps him going.
But it always balls down to his love for what's eternal.

I speak of a dedicated soldier of valor,
who is always girded in strong armor.
Many times have I wondered if he was a bachelor
Because he never takes a rest from labor.

A man whose vine is rooted in a strong foundation,
and structured to be lifted up in godly formation.
Respectful, resilient, loving, loyal, and kind,
of strong moral conviction and security in his mind, 
knowing who he is and what he could be,
having healthy relationships with his followers.

A man concerned about his community.
Who comprehends we live in a global society.
A man who gets involved and does not stay isolated,
As we are all a part of this world that God created.
A man who loves and respects his family and community.
A man strongly rooted, striding humbly and secure in his spirituality 

CORNELIUS!!!
